  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a medium saucepan, sauté the dates and unsalted butter over medium heat until caramelized.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the all-purpose flour, granulated sugar, salt, baking powder, and baking soda.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the large eggs, vanilla extract, and coconut milk.",
    "Add the wet ingredients to the dry ingredients and mix until a dough forms.",
    "Turn the dough onto a floured surface and knead for 5 minutes.",
    "Place the dough in a greased 9-inch round cake pan or tube pan.",
    "Bake for 35 minutes or until a toothpick inserted into the center comes out clean.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool for 10 minutes before serving.",
    "Dust with shredded coconut before serving.",
    "Serve warm.",
    "Cut into slices before serving."
  ],
